{"tid":1981491,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"謝sir讚揚同事拘捕攜帶氣油彈狂徒  成績振奮人心","createTime":"2020-04-20T16:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T05:37:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":143,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"c47f915b7818d6d71994d096a66af308b49e36a3","tid":1981491,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/04/20200414_CR_%E8%AC%9D%E6%8C%AF%E4%B8%AD1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F04%2F20200414_CR_%25E8%25AC%259D%25E6%258C%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD1.jpeg&h=f62ae180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尾二個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187ac3dbb5d53bcdf24973e14feeb723a72f8ce3","tid":1981491,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6269566-指限聚令後警隊巡查2萬次-謝振中感謝前線付出\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F6269566-%E6%8C%87%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E5%BE%8C%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%B7%A1%E6%9F%A52%E8%90%AC%E6%AC%A1-%E8%AC%9D%E6%8C%AF%E4%B8%AD%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E4%BB%98%E5%87%BA&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=4288ad6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6269566-指限聚令後警隊巡查2萬次-謝振中感謝前線付出</a>"},{"pid":"b474842548d085b54bb877da00a0e0f6d304f0e0","tid":1981491,"uid":320074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=3d53b76d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"604718804010e4f45cc679369f9d061ed5ef45cb","tid":1981491,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdee2212b183752c1dcefd7618808fc5295952b3","tid":1981491,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:44:48.000Z","msg":"NoSuchKeyThe specified key does not exist.web/404.htmEAD724A0C3A69E70RPuB3XhId8n+Or2CJpui1BgoOeBUvGmlODGzM+Ya1+aA24j8Fz1eAL4E3o7rzFd2OyD9yQY/yOg="},{"pid":"1c47d64f45ebc45185257ccbf145a866678629c8","tid":1981491,"uid":210612,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"難怪震怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c9b36